latte-dock (0.20.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * packaging/debian/: initial dh cmake recipe for Tier-1 .deb.
  * Build against the Debian testing Qt6/KF6/Plasma stack using
    debhelper/cmake with Ninja.  Runtime dependencies are resolved via
    shlibdeps plus the Plasma workspace stack needed by the QML shells.
  * Verified by building in a latte-debian:proto podman container and
    running the nested 000-smoke e2e recipe against the installed
    /usr/bin/latte-dock.

 -- Bree Spektor <maintainer@latte-dock.org>  Sun, 19 Jul 2026 20:38:33 +0000
